<hr data-start="179" data-end="182">
<h1 data-start="184" data-end="228">🦠 COVID-19 Dashboard – Step by Step Guide</h1>
<h2 data-start="230" data-end="248">🎯 Project Goal</h2>
<p data-start="249" data-end="276">Create a dashboard to show:</p>
<ul data-start="277" data-end="378">
<li data-start="277" data-end="296">
<p data-start="279" data-end="296">Total COVID cases</p>
</li>
<li data-start="297" data-end="305">
<p data-start="299" data-end="305">Deaths</p>
</li>
<li data-start="306" data-end="318">
<p data-start="308" data-end="318">Recoveries</p>
</li>
<li data-start="319" data-end="344">
<p data-start="321" data-end="344">Country-wise comparison</p>
</li>
<li data-start="345" data-end="378">
<p data-start="347" data-end="378">Trend over time (daily/monthly)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="380" data-end="383">
<h1 data-start="385" data-end="417">STEP 1️⃣ – Download Dataset 📥</h1>
<p data-start="418" data-end="465">Use ready dataset from GitHub or data websites:</p>
