<hr data-start="414" data-end="417">
<h1 data-start="419" data-end="436">Why it happens?</h1>
<p data-start="437" data-end="463">COVID dataset may contain:</p>
<ul data-start="464" data-end="538">
<li data-start="464" data-end="503">
<p data-start="466" data-end="503">country names with special characters</p>
</li>
<li data-start="504" data-end="521">
<p data-start="506" data-end="521">symbols in text</p>
</li>
<li data-start="522" data-end="538">
<p data-start="524" data-end="538">formatted data</p>
</li>
